               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"black\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"270\" y=\"15\" font-size=\"1em\">A</text> <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"134\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"134\" stroke=\"black\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"270\" y=\"134\" font-size=\"1em\">A</text> <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"114\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"114\" stroke=\"black\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"270\" y=\"114\" font-size=\"1em\">A</text> <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"64\" x2=\"115\" y2=\"64\" stroke=\"black\" />  <line x1=\"115\" y1=\"64\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"black\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"35\" y=\"50\" font-size=\"1em\">B</text>  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"36\" x2=\"155\" y2=\"36\" stroke=\"black\" /> <line x1=\"155\" y1=\"36\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"black\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"270\" y=\"50\" font-size=\"1em\">C</text> <circle cx=\"145\" cy=\"75\" r=\"30\"></circle> <circle cx=\"145\" cy=\"25\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#FF9999\"></circle><text x=\"143\" y=\"27\" font-size=\"1em\">-</text>  <circle cx=\"75\" cy=\"75\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#FF9999\"></circle><text x=\"73\" y=\"80\" font-size=\"1em\">-</text> <text x=\"120\" y=\"80\" font-size=\"1em\">+</text> <text x=\"140\" y=\"60\" font-size=\"1em\">+</text> <text x=\"140\" y=\"100\" font-size=\"1em\">+</text>  <text x=\"160\" y=\"80\" font-size=\"1em\">+</text> <circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"75\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#FF9999\"></circle><text x=\"202\" y=\"80\" font-size=\"1em\">-</text>  <circle cx=\"145\" cy=\"125\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#FF9999\"></circle><text x=\"143\" y=\"127\" font-size=\"1em\">-</text>  </svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 1</b>: Representación del modelo de Rutherford.</p>",
               "source": [],
